<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Darryl's Club</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            color: #000000;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .bw-image {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 400px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            border-radius: 10px;
            filter: grayscale(100%);
        }

        .link-btn {
            display: block;
            margin: 15px auto;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            width: 200px;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #ffffff;
            background-color: #000000;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            transition: 0.2s;
        }

        .link-btn:hover {
            background-color: #333333;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Darryl's Club</h1>

    <img class="bw-image" src="https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1389317036714496020/1409237685230632981/45d89f53a81186a8f41e24c048cd19ca.jpg" alt="Black and white image">

    <p>
        Hello, welcome to Darryl's club official website! Here you can find redirections to our Discord server & Null's brawl club. 
      For further assistance, please open a support ticket in the server.

      Please press the buttons below to be redirected to either the server or the club.
    </p>

    <a href="https://discord.gg/EnJApsrQKA" class="link-btn">Discord Server</a>
    <a href="https://link.nulls.gg/nb/invite/band/en?tag=QQ0LUQ998&token=p3n4y9uvzcr" class="link-btn">Null's Club</a>

</body>
</html>
